        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "“Habergeon” is an old English word, meaning armour for neck and breast.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Bows, and slings . . . stones.—For the light armed. (See margin.)",
