  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And Uzziah prepared for them throughout all the host,.... For every soldier in the army: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "shields and spears; defensive and offensive weapons, the one to cover and protect their bodies, the other to push and pierce their enemies: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and helmets, and habergeons; the first of these were a covering for the head in the day of battle, and the other coats of mail, to defend the body: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and bows; to shoot arrows out of: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and slings to cast stones; at which the Benjaminites formerly were very expert. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "and slings to cast stones; at which the Benjaminites formerly were very expert. ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
